file.name: post_data.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  version: '1.0.0'
  title: RESTBase post data storage module
  description: Revisioned post data storage with HTTP interface, backed by table storage
paths:
  /{bucket}:
    put:
      operationId: createBucket

  /{bucket}/:
    put:
      operationId: putRevision

  /{bucket}/{key}: &bucket_key
    get:
      operationId: getRevision
  /{bucket}/{key}/{tid}:
    <<: *bucket_key

  /{bucket}/hash:
    post:
      operationId: calculateHash

Error: parse: paths: /{bucket}: put: createBucket: parse path: path parameter not specified: "bucket"
